176 A.3d 225 ZIA H. SHAIKH, PLAINTIFF-MOVANT, v. LAURA L. GERMADNIG-SHAIKH, DEFENDANT.

M-458/459 September Term 2017

078989 December 8, 2017

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-458) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court’s order denying the motion for leave to appeal and proceed as indigent (M-459) is denied.
